CrossWords build tracker

Objective
- Create a polished CrossWords word-search game from the corrected PRD direction, commit it to the CrossWords repo, deploy it, and add it to the Fantom Zone homepage with Cloudflare routing.

Assumptions
- The intended game is a relaxed word-search experience: grid, word bank, swipe selection, validation, hints, no timer, no penalties, accessibility support, visual juice, themes, and progression.
- The CrossWords repo was empty on arrival, so the game was scaffolded as a greenfield Vite app.
- `fantomzone.app` should remain the arcade hub, with CrossWords added like the other games rather than replacing the home page.

Process log
- 2026-07-11: cloned repository and confirmed it had no commits.
- 2026-07-11: initially built a crossword-square version, then corrected direction after review.
- 2026-07-11: rebuilt the game to match the intended PRD direction: word-search grid, word bank, swipe validation, hints, no timer, no penalties, themed progression, and brighter visual design.
- 2026-07-11: verified the production build and fixed the Sites 404/blank-page issue by embedding the Vite build assets directly in the worker.
- 2026-07-11: committed and pushed CrossWords to GitHub at `workceostewart-lang/CrossWords`.
- 2026-07-11: deployed CrossWords to Sites version 4. Temporary live URL: `https://crosswords-fantomzone.unknownfigure.chatgpt.site/`.
- 2026-07-11: removed the accidental root-domain custom-domain attachment for `fantomzone.app` so CrossWords does not replace the arcade hub.
